- show battery level / voltage on remote startup
- attach interrupt(s) at start sending, detach when sending done

Menu():
OK Menu#A: lefthandmode On/Off

- Menu#B: receive current VESC-Data from RCV, show for 5s - go back to menu

- Menu#C: set current position as end position (RCV will stop rewinch when exceeding this position)

- Menu#D: PositionControl enable/disable

- Menu#E: Set ramps

OK Exit
